      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
        Points trend upward from bottom-left to top-right. As one variable
        increases, the other also increases. Example: study hours vs. exam
        scores.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
